[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":219},["Reactive",2],{"content-query-6vAmWQLT8p":3,"equal":33},{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":7,"description":5,"body":8,"_type":28,"_id":29,"_source":30,"_file":31,"_extension":32},"/credit","",false,"Credit",{"type":9,"children":10,"toc":25},"root",[11,16,21],{"type":12,"tag":13,"props":14,"children":15},"element","view-credit",{},[],{"type":12,"tag":17,"props":18,"children":20},"text-space",{"info":19},"* 由于本人并非专业人员，也未从事与安全研究员、渗透测试工程师或提供某种安全服务相关的工作，所以安全仅仅是我的个人兴趣。因此。在 'CREDIT' 卡片中发现的绝大部分漏洞都是歪打正着碰巧发现的。专业安全领域从业者、红队 / 蓝队等专业人士，以及硬件（HW）、CTF 等领域的工作者是我难以想象的高度，因此我无法媲美。在本网站有关安全的文章、CREDIT 以及本网站可能存在较大的书写问题，甚至在某些专业和领域的书面表达上可能质量较低，请谅解。\n\u003Cbr /> \u003Cbr />\n我深知在任何与技术相关的领域中，关注应用、效果以及解决问题是最重要的。任何过于花哨的设计或过多的描述都只是为了掩盖问题的本质。在技术领域中有一句流传的佳话：' 技术领域，菜是原罪 '。因此，我对安全领域的工作者们的工作充满向往。我一直认为编写安全报告是一件很酷的事情，尤其是在处理涉密信息时，这种感觉变得更加强烈（因为涉密信息是普通人难以接触的）。每当我有空闲时间，我都会浏览 Hack the Box Academy，体验专业的安全从业者所需要的课程或工作场景（这让我觉得安全从业者都很酷很帅）。\n\u003Cbr /> \u003Cbr />\n特别是在各种工具的开发中，在通过终端运行时我总能感受到技术上的纯粹美感。无论是交互式环境还是 GUI，与安全领域相关的一切都特别吸引我，它们的设计和代码简直是巧夺天工，是我此生渴望达到的目标。\n\u003Cbr /> \u003Cbr />\n我在 CREDIT 中筛选了我自 2019 年至今所提交且可以公开的漏洞。由于这些漏洞都是我在学生时代或年幼时无知而懵懂操作的结果，因此它们并不具备深度的技术描述或针对特定知识点的说明。如果您是技术或安全领域的从业者，或对相关行业有兴趣的人，很抱歉浪费了您 1~2 分钟的时间，对此我深感抱歉和愧疚。 ",[],{"type":12,"tag":22,"props":23,"children":24},"page-tips",{},[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":27},2,[],"markdown","content:credit.md","content","credit.md","md",[34,184,202],{"_path":35,"_dir":36,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":37,"description":5,"platform":38,"director":39,"types":40,"vulnerability":41,"release_date":42,"demo":43,"images":44,"body":45,"_type":28,"_id":182,"_source":30,"_file":183,"_extension":32},"/credit/github-misconfiguration","credit","GraphQL Misconfiguration in CWE-16 Github API","/images/credit/logo/hackerone.png","RHYME.Q","CREDIT","CWE-16","2023.12.04","https://hackerone.com/iepn","/images/credit/github.png",{"type":9,"children":46,"toc":180},[47,53,60,94,123,127,132,137,142,147,152,157,162,167,172,177],{"type":12,"tag":48,"props":49,"children":52},"page-img",{"img":50,"title":51,"url":43},"cwe-github/home","CWE-16 Github API",[],{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":55,"children":56},"p",{},[57],{"type":58,"value":59},"text","这是我第一次提交漏洞获得赏金和周边奖励的漏洞，所以我印象深刻。自我放弃安全路线以来，再一次发现较为知名厂商或平台的安全缺陷，可以当做是我的里程碑，但并不是终点。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":61,"children":62},{},[63,65,74,76,83,85,92],{"type":58,"value":64},"我很喜欢 Github 的章鱼猫，我也遇到过身边有好友将章鱼猫当做自己的头像来使用。封面上的章鱼猫来自 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":67,"children":71},"a",{"href":68,"rel":69},"https://octodex.github.com/",[70],"nofollow",[72],{"type":58,"value":73},"GitHub Octocats",{"type":58,"value":75}," 他的设计师是 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":77,"children":80},{"href":78,"rel":79},"https://jeejkang.com/Information",[70],[81],{"type":58,"value":82},"@James Kang",{"type":58,"value":84},"，您可以在 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":86,"children":89},{"href":87,"rel":88},"https://myoctocat.com/",[70],[90],{"type":58,"value":91},"myOctocat",{"type":58,"value":93}," 中创建属于自己的章鱼猫。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":95,"children":96},{},[97,99,106,108,113,114,121],{"type":58,"value":98},"在 2011 年中，GitHub 决定是时候升级他们的吉祥物 Octocat 了,所以 Github 邀请了很多设计师对章鱼猫进行创作，如 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":100,"children":103},{"href":101,"rel":102},"https://cameronmcefee.com/work/the-octocat/",[70],[104],{"type":58,"value":105},"Cameron McEfee",{"type":58,"value":107},"、",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":109,"children":111},{"href":78,"rel":110},[70],[112],{"type":58,"value":82},{"type":58,"value":107},{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":115,"children":118},{"href":116,"rel":117},"https://www.kimestoesta.com/",[70],[119],{"type":58,"value":120},"@KimEstoesta",{"type":58,"value":122}," …… 等",{"type":12,"tag":17,"props":124,"children":126},{"info":125},"从笔记本电脑上的贴花和衣服上的图形，到每个酒吧墙上、电线杆和街道标志上贴的贴纸，GitHub 的吉祥物 Octocat 是科技行业最知名的符号之一。@Cameron McEfee",[],{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":128,"children":129},{},[130],{"type":58,"value":131},"其中 James Kang 设计的章鱼猫之一的 Private Investocat 作为 Github Security - GitHub Bug Bounty 的标志性头像。",{"type":12,"tag":17,"props":133,"children":136},{"info":134,"img":135},"我很幸运在他们立项后的 13 年后，获得了它们的实体周边贴纸和胸针。他们的设计师是 @KimEstoesta 和 @Cameron McEfee","7/1",[],{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":138,"children":139},{},[140],{"type":58,"value":141},"同时我还收获到了来自 Github Bug Bounty 的 $200 USD ≈ 1,439 CNY 漏洞赏金，是我在安全道路中，第一次获得如此高昂的现金奖励。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":143,"children":144},{},[145],{"type":58,"value":146},"可惜我的定位一直就是团队中的 ACD（辅助）成长缓慢容易给单杀 0_0，一直处于打酱油的状态，有很多方面的技能树需要提升。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":148,"children":149},{},[150],{"type":58,"value":151},"自意识到安全是基于开发之下的存在后，我便开始尝试慢慢往开发方面转型，曾经我的老师之前说过：“如果真的有天赋，那不应该将时间投入到应用和框架当中，应该聚焦原理和底层逻辑的设计”。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":153,"children":154},{},[155],{"type":58,"value":156},"很明显我属于任何天赋为 0，基础薄弱，一生中无法有较大的成就。在我认识到自身的差距以后，我开始变得不善于与人交谈，退出了所有社区群组，慢慢提升自己。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":158,"children":159},{},[160],{"type":58,"value":161},"但等我真正见识到那些在各项比赛中大放异彩的选手后，以及在各类排行榜轻松拿下 10W、30W 奖励赏金的安全专家后，我开始没了当年的自信。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":163,"children":164},{},[165],{"type":58,"value":166},"慢慢的我意识到，有时候也许并不需要很好看的界面、很优雅的 Code，很完美的逻辑处理甚至是低的安全性，只需要一个噱头而已，让他们知道你可以就行了，并不需要做的很完美。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":168,"children":169},{},[170],{"type":58,"value":171},"我身边有很多例子，在发展到一定程度后，就会产生一种 “工匠精神”，开始意识到之前做的并不好，因此追求更高的标准。",{"type":12,"tag":54,"props":173,"children":174},{},[175],{"type":58,"value":176},"因此我一生中最敬佩的只有两种人，一种是追求这种境界成功的。而另一种是没有追求这种境界的，一直停留在最开始的阶段。",{"type":12,"tag":22,"props":178,"children":179},{},[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":181},[],"content:credit:github-misconfiguration.md","credit/github-misconfiguration.md",{"_path":185,"_dir":36,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":186,"description":5,"platform":187,"director":39,"types":40,"vulnerability":188,"release_date":189,"demo":190,"images":191,"body":192,"_type":28,"_id":200,"_source":30,"_file":201,"_extension":32},"/credit/edraw","亿图图示水印导出逻辑漏洞","/images/credit/logo/cnvd.png","CWE-703 | CNVD-2021-24498","2021.05.01","https://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/3173261","/images/credit/edraw.png",{"type":9,"children":193,"toc":198},[194],{"type":12,"tag":48,"props":195,"children":197},{"title":196},"CNVD-2021-24498h",[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":199},[],"content:credit:edraw.md","credit/edraw.md",{"_path":203,"_dir":36,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":204,"description":5,"platform":187,"director":39,"types":40,"vulnerability":205,"release_date":206,"demo":207,"images":208,"body":209,"_type":28,"_id":217,"_source":30,"_file":218,"_extension":32},"/credit/china-telecom","广东电信 IPTV 支付系统存在逻辑缺陷漏洞","CWE-703 | CNVD-2020-10601","2020.02.04","https://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/1976603","/images/credit/china-telecom.png",{"type":9,"children":210,"toc":215},[211],{"type":12,"tag":48,"props":212,"children":214},{"title":213},"CNVD-2020-10601",[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":216},[],"content:credit:china-telecom.md","credit/china-telecom.md",1710712221775]